{
  "_comment": [
    "Synthetic migration-replay fixture (PR0-D of #679). Tables are seeded",
    "in declaration order (FK parents first). Each row carries the HEAD",
    "column superset; the harness filters columns down to whatever exists",
    "at the staged version. min_version/max_version gate values whose",
    "legality changed over time:",
    "  - cards.role='plain' is trigger-rejected from 0037 on (max 36)",
    "  - legacy 'codex.job_requested' events are rewritten by 0038 (max 37)",
    "  - runtimes (0028+), operations (0029+), 'parked' phase (0042+)",
    "  - card_codex_threads exists 0025..0033, spec_push_queue 0022..0032",
    "Boundary values on purpose: NULLs, alias event kinds, every wave",
    "lifecycle state, exited/signal-killed terminals, spec runtime with",
    "and without an mcp token (0035/0036 transform the token-less one)."
